<!-- Game Description Table -->

<table class="tablestyle" id="table14" cellspacing="4" cellpadding="0">
	<tr>
		<td class="sectional">

<!-- Game Description Header -->
		
		<table class="headertable" id="table15" cellspacing="2" cellpadding="2">
			<tr>
				<td class="headercell">
				<img border="0" src="../../../images/headers/gamedes.jpg" width="240" height="33"></td>
			</tr>
		</table>

<!-- Game Description Sectional -->

<table border="0" width="100%" id="table16" cellpadding="0">
	<tr>
		<td style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; font-size: 8pt; color: #FFFFFF; font-weight: bold; text-align: left; background-color: #333333; border-left: 2px solid #000000; border-right: 2px solid #FFFFFF; border-top: 2px solid #000000; border-bottom: 2px solid #FFFFFF">
			<br>Dirt Jockey lets players control bulldozers, dump trucks, wheel loaders, hydraulic excavators, cranes, and other heavy-duty construction vehicles. Users will have to earn a license, then start construction on a gigantic department store. Four game modes -- qualification, build, free-play, and equipment rodeo -- ten machines, and multiplayer options keep young players busy.
                  <br><br>Build big machine muscle as you learn to operate heavy construction equipment that looks, feels, sounds and runs just like the real thing --- from rumbling bulldozers to hard-working dump trucks and high reaching cranes. Once you train to earn your construction licenses, you can start building a huge department store. So get in gear, move dirt and haul butt. Dirt Jockey fulfills the fantasy of operating heavy equipment for kids of all ages.
                  <br><br>Special Features
                  <br>- Four separate modes: Qualification, Build, Free-Play and Equipment Rodeo.
                  <br>- 10 different machines.
                  <br>- One or two players.
                  <br>- 4 separate modes: Qualification, Build, Free-Play and Equipment Rodeo
                  <br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;<u>Manufacturer's description:</u><br>
                  <br>Bulldozers. Cranes. Dump trucks. Gentlemen, start your engines.
                  <br><br>Operate heavy construction equipment that looks, feels, sounds and runs just like the real thing - from rumbling hydraulic excavators and hard-working dump trucks to wheel loaders, bulldozers and high-reaching cranes. Earn your construction licenses and start building.
                  <br><br>Learn to drive a crane, bulldozer, hydraulic excavator, wheel loader and dump truck-just like the ones at real construction sites.
                  <br><br>Test your skill in Equipment Rodeo, operating the excavator in 4 events: Treasure Hunt, Mountain Maker, Overdrive and Spin Touch.
                  <br><br>In Practice Mode, pick a machine and build a huge mountain of dirt or tear one down. You can even spell out your name in the mud.
                  <br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;<u>Features:</u><br>
			<ul><li>Third person perspective.</li>
			<li>3D graphics</li>
			<li>Cartoon graphics</li>
			<li>Heavy-duty construction vehicles theme.</li></ul>
</td>

	</tr>
	</table>
	       	</td>
     </tr>
</table>  

